    "body": "I figured out that this is related to signature verification in the Uniswap Permit contract. https://etherscan.io/address/0x000000000022d473030f116ddee9f6b43ac78ba3#code\r\n\r\naddress signer = ecrecover(hash, v, r, s);\r\nif (signer == address(0)) revert InvalidSignature();\r\nif (signer != claimedSigner) revert InvalidSigner();\r\n\r\nEssentially because the chain id was different the hash was different as well, and I suspect that the v,r,s generated by impersonate account did not necessarily satisfy the conditions. That's why I get the error.\r\n\r\nChanging the chain id lets it work.\r\n\r\n",
